Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy governs the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data of users of the
                Scoreboard: Score Keeper, developed by Techroz Solutions. We attach great importance to the protection
                of your
                privacy and are committed to processing your personal data in accordance with laws and the
                strictest privacy standards. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using our service. By
                using Scoreboard: Score Keeper, you accept the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
1. Collection and Use of Personal Data
1.1. We may also collect technical data, such as information about your device, IP address, log
            files, and cookies, to facilitate your use of Scoreboard: Score Keeper and analyze usage trends.
2. Protection and Storage of Personal Data
2.1. We take appropriate security measures to protect your personal data against unauthorized access,
            loss, alteration, or disclosure. We use encryption methods and advanced security protocols to ensure the
            confidentiality of your data.
2.2. Your personal data will be retained for the duration necessary for the purposes mentioned in this
            Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.
3. Sharing of Personal Data
3.1. We may share your personal data with third parties in the following cases:
a) When necessary to provide our services and respond to your requests.
b) When required by law, a court order, or a request from a competent government authority.
c) With your prior consent.
4. Cookies and Similar Technologies
4.1. We use cookies and other similar technologies to enhance your user experience, analyze usage
            trends, and personalize our service. You can configure your browser to refuse cookies, but this may
            limit certain features of Scoreboard: Score Keeper.
5. Links to Third-Party Sites
5.1. Scoreboard: Score Keeper may contain links to third-party websites. This Privacy Policy does not apply
            to those
            sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of those third-party sites before providing your
            personal data.
6. Modification of the Privacy Policy
6.1. We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. The modifications will take effect
            upon their publication on our website or Scoreboard: Score Keeper. We encourage you to regularly review this
            Privacy
            Policy to stay informed of any updates.
7. Contact
7.1. If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us
            at techrozsolutions.co@gmail.com
